{
  "stem": "27687.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My job was to work with about 30 Hollandase. from Holland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were free workers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were no-- not in a camp, nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were free workers, and--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Christian.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the-- the smallest one of these Hollanders must have been about six feet, the smallest one, so-- and the tallest one, must be over seven.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so we came to the-- they called it the [GERMAN], the-- the workplace.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they greeted us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Oh, yes, we need people and that, and we have so much work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But then they looked at us and they said, ah, I'll tell you what.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were about eight for this-- for this place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, they divided us, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So We were eight for this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they said to us, you know, we carry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You just load.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Load, you only have to take one sack, and we carry as much as we can.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, fine.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was very nice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we loaded them up, and most of them carried four sacks of cement.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, how can they do that?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the food was so good, the only thing we could not get, what they could get, is luxury stuff like ice cream and cakes and puddings and stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they were so nice, they brought us their stuff.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the food itself was very good.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The vegetables, the soups, and everything was fine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Who guarded you?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Over there?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "SS.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's the story.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One day on the way home, I heard the SS yelling at one guy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, I don't remember if that was one of our guys or if that was a Russian prisoner or if that was a French prisoner, because over there we all had the same clothes.",
      "word_count": 34
    }
  ],
